Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到达终点啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲也会去玩嘛 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是来参加“夏日祭”的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是来做什么的？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是光之美少女的潜入搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多拉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定会来寻找音符
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是赛莲 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 就到旁边去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,潜入搜查 加油哦 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,负向音调？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,负向音调呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,负向音调？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太过分了 姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是奏太惊讶过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是妖怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是粗糙的仿制品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点不礼貌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？难道艾莲也害怕妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有害怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那艾莲也来帮忙把
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在准备鬼屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是夏日祭的主打节目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不在此做个了结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不是女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲来扮伞妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,伞 伞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伞上长了眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这么生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲也一起来享受夏日祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要和你们一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的很担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咻~哆啰~！艾莲的弱点显现喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,完全变成了光之美少女...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有能打败赛莲的好作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那个 巴斯多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“夏日祭？”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找音符一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再好不过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定赛莲也会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不要命令我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让她们看到我那个样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太难为情了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哭吗？Lala
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是光之美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,呃~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lala Soso
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能站起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你受伤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好消毒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还疼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢...谢谢诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这所学校的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚从附近的镇上搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫王子正宗 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,黑川艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看你好像哭过的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲胆子很小？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米一点也不怕妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但赛莲从小时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就最讨厌妖怪了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米一点也不怕妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但赛莲晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢去洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要哈米陪她去 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米一点也不怕妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲一定是觉得难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以隐瞒了这件事 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是早点告诉我们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么之前都不告诉我们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米与赛莲约定谁也不告诉 喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我说出来了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩 就当作没有听到 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲一定真的生气了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,响和奏去向赛莲道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后和好吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易变成好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快点重归于好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,继续享受夏日祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好好加油！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...啊...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“妖怪”喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叛徒赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,居然有这样的弱点...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了好事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲 马上就让你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一直没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,终于和两个女孩成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 却被那两个人戏弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,戏弄？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕妖怪 因此被取笑...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和她们两个的关系变得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想和她们成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人真的是想戏弄你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地回想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地回想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这么一说...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人应该不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕妖怪这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是你的误会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友有时候 会互相看玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候会一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在困难的时候相互帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为朋友就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一定正担心着你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪 艾莲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出勇气来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,与她们和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想与你们和好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一起享受夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼节拍天使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不配做光之美少女
