Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喝喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,到达终点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁 万岁...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,愕 万岁 万岁 万岁...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这么兴高采烈...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小的艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但笑着的艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是最棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？音调精灵今天也不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是瞒着哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在吃好吃的东西 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 还在森林的树荫下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,友好地睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大家开心地购物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候被坏人袭击...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,危机的时候 大家也齐心协力...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把坏人给打败了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.57,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,组曲光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,枰砰啪砰♪音符精灵的大冒险喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让心中响起和声的力量吧
